Product: Clinora

Version: 1.0

Document Type: User Roles & Permission Matrix

Audience: Product Manager, Architects, Frontend, Backend, QA, DevOps

1. Purpose

The purpose of this document is to define the user roles within the Clinora platform and establish role-based access control (RBAC) for all application modules.

This document ensures that every user accesses only the information and functionality required for their responsibilities while maintaining patient privacy, tenant isolation, and platform security.

