6. Tenant Isolation Rules

Every authenticated request must include:

Tenant (Clinic)

Ôćô

User

Ôćô

Role

Ôćô

Permissions

Every database query must automatically filter using:

clinic_id

Example

Doctor from Clinic A

Cannot access

Patient from Clinic B

7. Authentication Rules

All users must authenticate using:

Email or Mobile Number
Password
JWT Access Token
Refresh Token

Future:

Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)
OTP Login
Biometric Login (Mobile)
8. Authorization Rules

Authorization is enforced at multiple levels.

UI

Users only see menus they are authorized to access.

Example

Patient

Appointments

Reports

Payments

Doctor menu never appears.

API

Every API validates:

Authentication

Ôćô

Role

Ôćô

Tenant

Ôćô

Permission
Database

Every query validates:

clinic_id

before returning data.

